OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAfter a fine
OL,6,Fand sunny evening, a dry night will
OL,7,Ffollow with clear spells and light
OL,8,Fwinds. Feeling warm and muggy,
OL,9,Fespecially in the south and east,
OL,10,Fbringing difficult sleeping conditions.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FA little showery rain is
OL,13,Fpossible through the middle of the
OL,14,Fday, otherwise mostly dry and bright
OL,15,Fwith sunny spells. Feeling hot and
OL,16,Fhumid, especially in the south and
OL,17,Feast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
